<sec>
<st>
Early life</st>
<p>

Born in  Oklahoma City, Yeagley is an enrolled member of the <ethnic_group wordnetid="107967382" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../001/54001.xml">
Comanche</link></ethnic_group>
 Nation, based in <village wordnetid="108672738" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../131/130131.xml">
Lawton</link></village>
, Oklahoma, and claims descent from <physical_entity wordnetid="100001930" confidence="0.8">
<military_action wordnetid="100952963" confidence="0.8">
<group_action wordnetid="101080366" confidence="0.8">
<person wordnetid="100007846" confidence="0.8">
