<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../273/34273.xml">
Yale University</link></university>
, a Master of Arts in Literature and History from <university wordnetid="108286163" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../730/42730.xml">
Emory University</link></university>
 (1981), an Artist Diploma in Piano Performance and Pedagogy from the <university wordnetid="108286163" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../489/633489.xml">
Hartt School of Music</link></university>
