<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../405/259405.xml">
Andover</link></village>
, Massachusetts (1990); President's Church in <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../775/3775.xml">
Boston</link>, Massachusetts in (1990); and University of Arizona Art Museum in <village wordnetid="108672738" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../180/57180.xml">
