, <symbol wordnetid="106806469" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../961/1961.xml">
Arizona</link></symbol>
 (1994).  All pencil drawings and lectures were created by Yeagley, and music was provided by <physical_entity wordnetid="100001930" confidence="0.8">
