.  This, along with his <it>10 Etudes for Native American Flute</it>, can be found on his 2004 album <it>Awakenings</it>.  He was also commissioned by José Cordero, Founder and President of the Native Sun Symphony Orchestra, to compose that organization's anthem. Yeagley's music for Native American flute has also been recorded by <physical_entity wordnetid="100001930" confidence="0.8">
