<p>

Also in 1999, Yeagley was commissioned by the late Jack P. Eisner for the world's first grand opera about the Jewish <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../793/10396793.xml">
Holocaust</link> of <military_action wordnetid="100952963" confidence="0.8">
